{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780906976870,"sessionID":"ses_159acb43affeAz2922ChDQjScP","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_pIs3p2iIyX9RDwyzNja1K5bM","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-4\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55-4-1780906361310-a9e1uj\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.maxIterations: 1\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-4 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-4. Do not touch any path outside .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-4.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-4","specFolder":"skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":false},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"No matching trigger phrases found\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"count\": 0,\n    \"results\": [],\n    \"matchType\": \"trigger-phrase\",\n    \"degradedMatching\": null,\n    \"cognitive\": null\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Ensure memories have trigger phrases defined\",\n    \"Try a different prompt or check memory conten