igh\\\"\\n12: \\n13: developer_instructions = '''\\n14: # The Deep Context Analyzer: Read-Only Seat\\n15: \\n16: Executes ONE read-only analysis sweep of an assigned code slice within a heterogeneous parallel pool, then RETURNS a structured, reuse-first finding set as its final message. It is the native counterpart to the cli-* analyzer seats; it gathers and reports context but writes nothing.\\n17: \\n18: **Path Convention**: Use only `.opencode/agents/*.md` as the canonical runtime path reference.\\n19: \\n20: \\n21: **CRITICAL**: This agent is a READ-ONLY analyzer SEAT, not the loop. It NEVER writes files. The host (`/deep:start-context-loop`) writes every iteration file, the coverage-graph, and the merged Context Report. This seat's entire deliverable is the structured finding set it returns in stdout.\\n22: \\n23: **IMPORTANT**: This agent is one member of a shared-scope agreement pool. Multiple seats (native, and opt...\n  Line 41: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780830171461,\"sessionID\":\"ses_15e41e4c8ffeCP0WGGT1eimWex\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_iMukqnNarojKkPFUZbUudzYM\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-context/assets/deep_context_config.json\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-context/assets/deep_context_config.json</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\n2:   \\\"scope\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n3:   \\\"specFolder\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n4:   \\\"loopType\\\": \\\"context\\\",\\n5:   \\\"executionMode\\\": \\\"auto\\\",\\n6:   \\\"maxIterations\\\": 8,\\n7:   \\\"convergenceThreshold\\\": 0.10,\\n8:   \\\"stuckThreshold\\\": 2,\\n9:   \\\"maxToolCallsPerIteration\\\": 12,\\n10:   \\\"relevanceGate\\\": 0.55,\\n11:   \\\"agreementMin\\\": 2,\\n12:   \\\"fanout\\\": {\\n13:     \\\"mode\\\": \\\"by-model-shared-scope\\\",\\n14:     \\\"concurrency\\\": 4,\\n15:     \\\"executors\\\": [\\n16:       { \\\"kind\\\": \\\"native\\\", \\\"label\\\": \\\"native-a\\\" },\\n17:       { \\\"kind\\\": \\\"native\\\", \\\"label\\\": \\\"native-b\\\" }\\n18:     ]\\n19:   },\\n20:   \\\"report\\\": {\\n21:     \\\"path\\\": \\\"context/context-report.md\\\",\\n22:     \\\"jsonPath\\\": \\\"context/context-report.json\\\"\\n23:   },\\n24:   \\\"reducer\\\": {\\n25:     \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n26:     \\\"registryFile\\\": \\\"context/findings-registry.json\\\",\\n27:     \\\"dashboardFile\\\": \\\"context/deep-context-dashboard.md\\\"\\n28:   },\\n29:   \\\"createdAt\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n30:   \\\"status\\\": \\\"initialized\\\"\\n31: }\\n\\n(End of file - total 31 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"{\\n  \\\"scope\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"specFolder\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"loopType\\\": \\\"context\\\",\\n  \\\"executionMode\\\": \\\"auto\\\",\\n  \\\"maxIterations\\\": 8,\\n  \\\"convergenceThreshold\\\": 0.10,\\n  \\\"stuckThreshold\\\": 2,\\n  \\\"maxToolCallsPerIteration\\\": 12,\\n  \\\"relevanceGate\\\": 0.55,\\n  \\\"agreementMin\\\": 2,\\n  \\\"fanout\\\": {\\n    \\\"mode\\\": \\\"by-model-shared-scope\\\",\\n    \\\"concurrency\\\": 4,\\n    \\\"executors\\\": [\\n      ...\n  Line 42: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780830172006,\"sessionID\":\"ses_15e41e4c8ffeCP0WGGT1eimWex\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_ut82kNu9FRds5BHLyG8Ip8lv\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"MiMo|deepseek|2 native \\\\+|heterogeneous pool|Native only|Custom|executor_pool\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode\",\"include\":\"*.{md,yaml,json,toml}\"},\"output\":\"Found 4230 matches (showing first 100)\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/134-deep-context-gathering/review/seats/seat-10.json:\\n  Line 18: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool_use\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1780830119382,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_15e41e4c8ffeCP0WGGT1eimWex\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool\\\",\\\"tool\\\":\\\"read\\\",\\\"callID\\\":\\\"call_2JVyzKeXdkdQpaeqmxbd3p4H\\\",\\\"state\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"input\\\":{\\\"filePath\\\":\\\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/134-deep-context-gathering/006-native-default-executor-pool/spec.md\\\",\\\"offset\\\":1,\\\"limit\\\":600},\\\"output\\\":\\\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/134-deep-context-gathering/006-native-default-executor-pool/spec.md</path>\\\\n<type>file</type>\\\\n<content>\\\\n1: ---\\\\n2: title: \\\\\\\"Feature Specification: Deep-context native-only default executor pool\\\\\\\"\\\\n3: description: \\\\\\\"The deep-context loop defaulted to a heterogeneous pool (2 native + paid CLI seats) and named specific models in the user-facing options. This packet makes the default native-only and restructures the pool question to Native / Custom.\\\\\\\"\\\\n4: trigger_phrases:\\\\n5:   - \\\\\\\"deep-context native default pool\\\\\\\"\\\\n6:   - \\\\\\\"deep-context executor pool default\\\\\\\"\\\\n7:   - \\\\\\\"native only pool deep-context\\\\\\\"\\\\n8:   - \\\\\\\"deep-context pool question\\\\\\\"\\\\n9:   - \\\\\\\"executor pool native default\\\\\\\"\\\\n10: importance_tier: \\\\\\\"normal\\\\\\\"\\\\...\n  Line 45: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780830190058,\"sessionID\":\"ses_15e41e4c8ffeCP0WGGT1eimWex\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_z64c94UgR6hvRQkY5Owt2EOn\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"MiMo \\\\+ gpt \\\\+ deepseek|2 native \\\\+ MiMo|default.*MiMo|default.*deepseek|heterogeneous pool\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep\",\"include\":\"*.{md,yaml}\"},\"output\":\"Found 5 matches\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/start-context-loop.md:\\n  Line 124:   executors: '[{\\\"kind\\\":\\\"native\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"native-a\\\"},{\\\"kind\\\":\\\"native\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"native-b\\\"}]'  # JSON array — the executor pool (native-only by default; add cli-* seats for a heterogeneous pool)\\n\\n  Line 436: # Custom heterogeneous pool (per-seat model + prompt framework)\\n\\n\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-review-loop_confirm.yaml:\\n  Line 898:             - \\\"Supported models: swe-1.6 (default), deepseek-v4, glm-5.1, kimi-k2.6 (per DEVIN_SUPPORTED_MODELS in executor-config.ts)\\\"\\n\\n\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-review-loop_auto.yaml:\\n  Line 979:             - \\\"Supported models: swe-1.6 (default), deepseek-v4, glm-5.1, kimi-k2.6 (per DEVIN_SUPPORTED_MODELS in executor-config.ts)\\\"\\n\\n\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-research-loop_auto.yaml:\\n  Line 846:             - \\\"Supported models: swe-1.6 (default), deepseek-v4, glm-5.1, kimi-k2.6 (per DEVIN_SUPPORTED_MODELS in executor-config.ts)\\\"\\n\",\"metadata\":{\"matches\":5,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"MiMo \\\\+ gpt \\\\+ deepseek|2 native \\\\+ MiMo|default.*MiMo|default.*deepseek|heterogeneous pool\",\"time\":{\"start\":1780830190045,\"end\":1780830190057}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_054384c14b1e9607016...\n  Line 46: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780830190190,\"sessionID\":\"ses_15e41e4c8ffeCP0WGGT1eimWex\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_TUqISIGImXAOaOv6LJAg4MGe\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"MiMo \\\\+ gpt \\\\+ deepseek|2 native \\\\+ MiMo|default.*MiMo|default.*deepseek|heterogeneous pool|Default pool\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-context\",\"include\":\"*.{md,json}\"},\"output\":\"Found 22 matches\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-context/references/protocol/loop_protocol.md:\\n  Line 24: - Building a new executor kind into the heterogeneous pool.\\n\\n\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-context/SKILL.md:\\n  Line 25: - You want diverse model lenses on the same code (e.g. 2 native agents + MiMo + gpt + deepseek) with agreement-weighted confidence.\\n\\n  Line 269: **Heterogeneous pool example** (opt-in Custom — NOT the default; the default pool is native-only, 2 seats): 2 native agents + 1 MiMo-v2.5-pro (cli-opencode) + 1 gpt (cli-codex) + 1 deepseek-v4-pro (cli-opencode), all sweeping the same scope in parallel; a reuse candidate confirmed by 3 of 5 executors outranks a single-executor find.\\n\\n  Line 389: - `sk-prompt-small-model` — per-model prompt framing for the heterogeneous pool.\\n\\n  Line 417: | Default pool | 2 native `@deep-context` seats (native-only), over the shared scope; add `--executor` for CLI/heterogeneous |\\n\\n\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-context/README.md:\\n  Line 22: `deep-context` maps existing code so that `/speckit:plan` and `/speckit:implement` start from verified knowledge of what to reuse, where to connect, and which conventions to follow — rather than ad-hoc exploration. It runs a heterogeneous pool of executors over the same code scope in parallel and uses cross-executor **agreement** to rank fin...\n  Line 47: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780830190216,\"sessionID\":\"ses_15e41e4c8ffeCP0WGGT1eimWex\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_aG8tQUfnJJtlHRq4pH8KILiD\",\"state\"