e review (use `sk-code-review` instead)\\n- Known issues that just need fixing (go directly to impleme...\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780830106978,\"sessionID\":\"ses_15e41e4c1ffeogTFdTfQvTzxkC\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_klJiSCeHeTrbZseNpttKjApS\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/start-research-loop.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":250},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/start-research-loop.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: description: Autonomous deep-research loop: iterative investigation with convergence detection. Modes :auto, :confirm.\\n3: argument-hint: \\\"<topic> [:auto|:confirm] [--max-iterations=N] [--convergence=N] [--executor=<type> [--model=X] [--count=N] [--label=X] ...] [--executors=<json>] [--concurrency=N] (:auto supports PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS: prompt-body block for non-interactive setup)\\\"\\n4: allowed-tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Grep, Glob, Task, WebFetch, memory_context, memory_search, code_graph_query, code_graph_context\\n5: ---\\n6: \\n7: > **Code Graph ownership:** `code_graph_query` and `code_graph_context` stay stable MCP tool IDs; implementation and docs now live under `.opencode/skills/system-code-graph/`.\\n8: \\n9: > **EXECUTION PROTOCOL -- READ FIRST**\\n10: >\\n11: > This command runs a structured YAML workflow. Do NOT dispatch agents from this document.\\n12: >\\n13: > **YOUR FIRST ACTION (two HARD-BLOCK gates — do them in order, skip neither):**\\n14: > 1. Run Phase 0: @general agent self-verification (below)\\n15: > 2. Run the Unified Setup Phase (BLOCKED gate) in this Markdown entrypoint and resolve:\\n16: >    - `research_topic`\\n17: >    - `spec_folder`\\n18: >    - `execution_mode`\\n19: >    - `maxIterations`\\n20: >    - `convergenceThreshold`\\n21: >