w and quality auditing, see `/deep:start-review-loop`.\\n275: \\n276: ## Convergence Threshold Semantics\\n277: \\n278: **Default:** 0.05 on newInfoRatio (fully-new=1.0, partially-new=0.5, +0.10 simplicity bonus, capped 1.0)\\n279: \\n280: **Semantic:** `convergenceThreshold` compares newly discovered information against accumulated research knowledge with nega...\n  Line 13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780830114028,\"sessionID\":\"ses_15e41e4c1ffeogTFdTfQvTzxkC\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_ymvrxLVhNiZ1byh8HZduG6NC\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/start-review-loop.md\",\"offset\":251,\"limit\":300},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/start-review-loop.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n251:      B) Interactive -- pause at each iteration for review\\n252: \\n253:    Q3. Max Iterations (if not set via flag):\\n254:      Default is 7 for review. Change? [Enter number or press enter for default]\\n255: \\n256:    Q-Exec. Executor (optional, press enter for default):\\n257:      A) Native (default) — dispatch via @deep-review agent with Opus.\\n258:      B) cli-codex — `codex exec` with --model X -c model_reasoning_effort -c service_tier.\\n259:      C) cli-gemini — `gemini \\\"PROMPT\\\" -m gemini-3.1-pro-preview -y -o text`. Single supported model currently. No reasoning-effort or service-tier.\\n260:      D) cli-claude-code — `claude -p \\\"PROMPT\\\" --model X --permission-mode acceptEdits` with optional --effort. No service-tier.\\n261:      E) cli-opencode — `opencode run --model X --format json --dangerously-skip-permissions --pure --dir {repo_root} [--variant Y] \\\"PROMPT\\\" </dev/null` (no `--agent`: current opencode rejects top-level `--agent general` — default agent runs; required for MiniMax/Xiaomi token-plan models). `reasoningEffort` maps to `--variant`. No service-tier.\\n262:      F) cli-devin — `devin --print --prompt-file ... --model X --permission-mode auto`. Default model swe-1.6. No reasoning-effort or service-tier.\\n263: \\n264:    Reply format examples:\\n265:    - `\\\"skill:deep-research, B, all, A, A\\\"`\\n266:    - `\\\"review the deep-review packet output, E, correctness security, B, B, 5\\\"`\\n267:    - `\\\"Review review/review-report.md contra...\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 13373 matches (13273 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":13373,"truncated":true},"title":"CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR|CODEX_PROJECT_DIR|DEVIN_PROJECT_DIR|\\$PWD|/opt/homebrew|/Users/|n/bin/node","time":{"start":1780907143324,"end":1780907143788}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_06e30782004681f5016a267c86d9a881919f95ccb1addaa369"}},"id":"prt_ea6567044001zo4MAT6UmSQEeH","sessionID":"ses_159acb43affeAz2922ChDQjScP","messageID":"msg_ea6563c07001e5yo4SpSxHFPvR"}}
